description: Plaintiff(s): Chase Mellen (a lawyer) and his wife Ronnie Mellen. Defendant: Masood Azizi (carpet shop owner). The case: The plaintiffs are suing the defendant $5000 for a refund over an expensive Chinese Nichols carpet he sold them. The plaintiffs claim the carpet was a fake. The outcome: Case is dismissed.
